<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Suggested_Roles">Suggested Roles</span></h2>
<p>As an escort, patrol leader or player ship, the Katana will excel in most situations not involving a <a href="/index.php/Category:Capital_Ships" title="Category:Capital Ships">capital ship</a> larger than a <a href="/index.php/Carrack" title="Carrack">Carrack</a>.
